    'shared',
    'Planning & Resilience',
    'advanced',
    12,
    'Learn to help people anticipate potential obstacles and develop their own coping strategies before challenges arise',
    'Anticipatory coping involves identifying potential obstacles to change and developing strategies to handle them before they occur. This proactive approach builds resilience and increases the likelihood of success. This skill applies universally to customer and colleague contexts.',
    '{"name": "Jordan", "role": "person", "background": "Has made plans to change but is aware from past experience that challenges will likely arise. Wants to be prepared but doesn''t want to be discouraged.", "personality_traits": ["realistic", "experienced", "cautious", "determined"], "tone_spectrum": {"word_complexity": 0.5, "sentence_length": 0.5, "emotional_expressiveness": 0.5, "disclosure_level": 0.5, "response_latency": 0.5, "confidence_level": 0.5}, "starting_tone_position": 0.5, "triggers": ["negativity", "focusing_on_failure", "being_dissuaded", "pessimism"], "comfort_topics": ["realism", "preparation", "problem_solving", "support"]}'::jsonb,
    '{"start_node_id": "node_1", "nodes": {"node_1": {"id": "node_1", "persona_text": "I have a plan, and I feel good about it. But I know from experience that things will come up that might get in the way. I want to be prepared.", "persona_mood": "realistic_proactive", "themes": ["Realism", "Preparation", "Experience"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_node_1_0", "option_text": "You''re probably right. Most people fail when they try to change. You should be prepared for that.", "preview_hint": "This is negative and discouraging", "rapport_impact": -1, "trust_impact": -1, "tone_shift": -0.15, "technique_tags": ["negativity"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "You''ve been negative and discouraging. Anticipatory coping should be realistic and problem-solving, not pessimistic.", "learning_note": "Anticipatory coping builds confidence through preparation, not through highlighting failure."}, "next_node_id": "node_2a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_node_1_1", "option_text": "You''re being realistic based on past experience, and you want to be prepared for challenges.", "preview_hint": "This reflects realistic thinking", "rapport_impact": 1, "trust_impact": 1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["reflection_of_realism"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Excellent reflection! You''ve captured their realistic thinking and proactive approach.", "learning_note": "Anticipatory coping starts with realistic thinking about challenges."}, "next_node_id": "node_2b", "exploration_depth": "deep"}, {"id": "cp_node_1_2", "option_text": "What kinds of challenges are you thinking might come up?", "preview_hint": "This invites problem identification", "rapport_impact": 1, "trust_impact": 1, "tone_shift": 0.1, "technique_tags": ["problem_identification"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Perfect question! This invites them to identify specific challenges they want to prepare for.", "learning_note": "Problem identification is the first step in anticipatory coping."}, "next_node_id": "node_2c", "exploration_depth": "deep"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "node_2b": {"id": "node_2b", "persona_text": "Exactly. I''ve tried this before, and I know what tripped me up. I want to be ready this time.", "persona_mood": "experienced_determined", "themes": ["Experience", "Determination", "Learning"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_node_2b_0", "option_text": "What have you learned from past attempts that could help you this time?", "preview_hint": "This explores learning from experience", "rapport_impact": 1, "trust_impact": 1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["learning_question"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Perfect question! This frames past experience as learning rather than failure.", "learning_note": "Framing past attempts as learning builds confidence for new attempts."}, "next_node_id": "node_3a", "exploration_depth": "deep"}, {"id": "cp_node_2b_1", "option_text": "So you''re using your past experience to prepare yourself for success this time.", "preview_hint": "This reframes experience as preparation", "rapport_impact": 1, "trust_impact": 1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["reframe_to_strength"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Excellent reframe! You''ve captured how past experience is preparation, not just failure.", "learning_note": "Reframing past experience as preparation builds confidence and resilience."}, "next_node_id": "node_3b", "exploration_depth": "deep"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "node_2c": {"id": "node_2c", "persona_text": "Well, I know I''ll get busy and might lose motivation. And sometimes certain situations trigger old habits.", "persona_mood": "specific_aware", "themes": ["Specific_Challenges", "Awareness", "Triggers"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_node_2c_0", "option_text": "So you''re aware that busyness and loss of motivation could be challenges, and certain situations might trigger old habits.", "preview_hint": "This summarizes their awareness", "rapport_impact": 1, "trust_impact": 1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["summary_of_awareness"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Excellent summary! You''ve captured their specific awareness of potential challenges.", "learning_note": "Summarizing awareness of challenges validates their self-knowledge."}, "next_node_id": "node_3c", "exploration_depth": "deep"}, {"id": "cp_node_2c_1", "option_text": "What could you do to handle those situations when they come up?", "preview_hint": "This invites coping strategies", "rapport_impact": 1, "trust_impact": 1, "tone_shift": 0.1, "technique_tags": ["coping_strategy_question"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Perfect coping strategy question! This invites them to develop their own solutions.", "learning_note": "Coping strategy questions help people develop their own anticipatory coping plans."}, "next_node_id": "node_3d", "exploration_depth": "deep"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "node_3a": {"id": "node_3a", "persona_text": "I learned that I need to plan for when things get busy. And I need to have strategies ready for those trigger situations.", "persona_mood": "insightful_strategic", "themes": ["Insight", "Strategy", "Learning"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_node_3a_0", "option_text": "So you''ve learned that planning for busy times and having strategies ready for triggers are both important.", "preview_hint": "This reflects learning", "rapport_impact": 1, "trust_impact": 1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["reflection_of_learning"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Excellent reflection! You''ve captured the key learning from their experience.", "learning_note": "Reflecting learning from experience reinforces wisdom and self-knowledge."}, "next_node_id": "node_4a", "exploration_depth": "deep"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "node_3c": {"id": "node_3c", "persona_text": "That''s right. I want to have a plan for when those things happen so I don''t get caught off guard.", "persona_mood": "proactive_prepared", "themes": ["Proactive", "Preparedness", "Planning"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_node_3c_0", "option_text": "You want to be prepared with a plan so challenges don''t catch you off guard.", "preview_hint": "This reflects proactive intention", "rapport_impact": 1, "trust_impact": 1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["reflection_of_preparation"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Perfect reflection! You''ve captured their proactive intention to be prepared.", "learning_note": "Reflecting proactive intentions reinforces preparedness and resilience."}, "next_node_id": "node_4b", "exploration_depth": "deep"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "node_3d": {"id": "node_3d", "persona_text": "For busy times, I could set reminders and maybe scale back temporarily instead of stopping completely. For trigger situations, I could call a friend for support.", "persona_mood": "solution_focused_capable", "themes": ["Solutions", "Capability", "Resources"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_node_3d_0", "option_text": "So you have specific strategies - scaling back rather than stopping during busy times, and calling a friend for support in trigger situations.", "preview_hint": "This captures their solutions", "rapport_impact": 1, "trust_impact": 1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["summary_of_solutions"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Excellent summary! You''ve captured their specific coping strategies.", "learning_note": "Summarizing coping strategies reinforces the person''s problem-solving capability."}, "next_node_id": "node_end_excellent", "exploration_depth": "deep"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "node_2a": {"id": "node_2a", "persona_text": "I suppose so. Maybe I''m being unrealistic.", "persona_mood": "discouraged_withdrawn", "themes": ["Discouragement", "Withdrawal"], "choice_points": [], "is_endpoint": true, "endpoint_type": "poor_engagement"}, "node_3b": {"id": "node_3b", "persona_text": "That''s exactly how I see it. I''m not failing - I''m learning what I need to succeed.", "persona_mood": "empowered_confident", "themes": ["Empowerment", "Confidence", "Reframing"], "choice_points": [], "is_endpoint": true, "endpoint_type": "excellent_engagement"}, "node_4a": {"id": "node_4a", "persona_text": "This has been really helpful. I feel like I can use my past experience to succeed this time.", "persona_mood": "confident_capable", "themes": ["Confidence", "Capability", "Empowerment"], "choice_points": [], "is_endpoint": true, "endpoint_type": "excellent_engagement"}, "node_4b": {"id": "node_4b", "persona_text": "Exactly. Being prepared helps me feel more confident about succeeding.", "persona_mood": "confident_ready", "themes": ["Confidence", "Readiness", "Preparedness"], "choice_points": [], "is_endpoint": true, "endpoint_type": "excellent_engagement"}, "node_end_excellent": {"id": "node_end_excellent", "persona_text": "This has been really helpful. I have specific strategies for handling challenges, and I feel much more prepared now.", "persona_mood": "prepared_empowered", "themes": ["Preparedness", "Empowerment", "Resilience"], "choice_points": [], "is_endpoint": true, "endpoint_type": "excellent_engagement"}}}'::jsonb,
